## Known limitations

- Velocity readings are approximate (±50%). Accurate VBT requires sensor fusion
  with complementary filtering, calibrated industrial-grade IMUs, and rotation
  compensation — beyond the scope of this v1 build.
- Designed for non-rotational lifts (squat, deadlift, bench). Olympic lifts not
  supported in this version.

## Future work
- Implement Madgwick or Mahony filter for full sensor fusion
- Add gyro-based motion-detection gating to prevent gravity contamination